document.masterDocTitle: Larval Psephenidae (Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) of Thailand: Annotated List and Illustrated Key to Genera

mods:titleInfo.mods:title: Larval Psephenidae (Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) of Thailand: Annotated List and Illustrated Key to Genera

subSubSection.paragraph: Discussion. Larvae of this type were found in a variety of localities, mostly in the western half of the country. This genus differs from all other described genera by the sutural configuration on the prothorax ( Fig. 22 ) and the lack of a gap between paratergites 6 and 7. This larva is not included in the key because it might represent a new genus or an undescribed member of an existing genus not known from Thailand .
